            "<p><strong>Summarize (Orchestrating the Discussion)</strong></p><p><em>Discussing Solutions and Strategies </em></p><p>Discuss Baruti&#x27;s science grades. Ask students to analyze the percentages in the grades.</p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "TILEKcqDryoCE4M1",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p><strong>Suggested Questions </strong></p><ul><li>Baruti only missed 1 point on each assignment. Does that make all of his grades the same? </li></ul>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "TILEsTGkpR30JJKf",
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>No. He only missed 1 point, but the number of points changes, so that changes his grade from assignment to assignment. </p>"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "dKCc4bMocCMCZRdt",
        "title": "Text 17",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<ul><li>Which of the assignments has the lowest percentage grade? </li></ul>"
          ]
